### Output:
```java
public String extractTemplate(String message) {
    String[] splitted = message.split(" ");
    String result = String.format("Received block %s of size %s from %s",
        splitted[0].substring(splitted[0].indexOf("_") + 1),
        splitted[1],
        splitted[2]);
    return result;
}
